data.description: Gorgeous traditional home located in Moss Bluff, LA! This beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bath home is the definition of style and grace. Meticulously maintained, this over 2100 sq ft home proudly boasts a one level split floor plan, large open concept living room/kitchen with a massive granite laid sit-up island, and dedicated dining space that offers the perfect space for large gatherings, family game and movie nights, or meals enjoyed by all. The roomy kitchen is designed with storage and style in mind, with tons of upper and lower cabinets, storage on the island, and a separate pantry space, all pleasantly presented in on-trend neutral color schemes.  Nearby, an interior laundry room offers additional storage and convenience. A sizable 15X16 primary suite sits to the rear, and provides ample privacy for the owner, in addition to a luxurious and spacious ensuite with large double vanity, separate shower, freestanding soaking tub, and large walk-in closet. On the other side of the home, 2 more 14X15 bedrooms and a large bathroom round out this spacious homes offerings.  In addition to the "under roof" amenities, you will notice a large rear patio, fully fenced in back yard, ample 2 car garage with a large storage room, perfect for seasonal storage items, tools, or even hobbies! Located in Flood X, where flood insurance is typically not required, this home is ready for its new owners to enjoy!  Seller has an assumable mortgage in the low 2% interest range. Finally, all appliances are to remain, including refrigerator and washer and dryer, making this the perfect turnkey home!  Call or setup your showing today!
